### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Générer une facture depuis un devis (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin-generate-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Générer une facture depuis un événement
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin-generate-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: paramètres manquants
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin-generate-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: événement sans devis accepté
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin-generate-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-without-accepted-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: accès non autorisé
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin-generate-invoice
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

